text: Holly Robinson is a fictional Batman character from DC Comics who is friends with Selina Kyle. She is the crime-partner of Catwoman for bank robbery. For a short while, she became Catwoman because Selina had her first baby. In some appearances, she is a lesbian. == In other media == She was played by Juno Temple as Jen in The Dark Knight Rises.
